RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.COUNTERPARTY,/*B.SHORT_NAME*/B.customer_name1||' '||B.customer_name2 as SHORT_NAME FROM LBTBS_PART_PROC_STAT A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER B WHERE a.BORROWER_REF_NO= ? AND A.COUNTERPARTY = B.CUSTOMER_NO and A.COUNTERPARTY not in (SELECT A.COUNTERPARTY FROM LBTBS_PART_PROC_STAT A, TLTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER B WHERE a.BORROWER_REF_NO = ? AND A.COUNTERPARTY = B.POSITION_IDENTIFIER)AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM LBTBS_COLL_PARTICIPANT C WHERE c.CONTRACT_REF_NO = a.BORROWER_REF_NO AND c.PARTICIPANT = a.COUNTERPARTY AND c.EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LBTBS_COLL_PARTICIPANT WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = c.CONTRACT_REF_NO)) UNION SELECT A.COUNTERPARTY,B.POSITION_IDENTIFIER_DESC FROM LBTBS_PART_PROC_STAT A, TLTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER B WHERE a.BORROWER_REF_NO = ? AND A.COUNTERPARTY = B.POSITION_IDENTIFIER AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM LBTBS_COLL_PARTICIPANT C WHERE c.CONTRACT_REF_NO = a.BORROWER_REF_NO AND c.PARTICIPANT = a.COUNTERPARTY AND c.EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LBTBS_COLL_PARTICIPANT WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = c.CONTRACT_REF_NO))

RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LBTBS_COLL_PARTICIPANT WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = LBTB_COLL_PARTICIPANT.CONTRACT_REF_NO)
